reviewText:
I played this game on a friend's pc and I love this game, I was so excited to get it, but I didn't see know that it doesn't work through Steam for Windows 8 until afterwards. I found this forum though that helped me fix it in a way.

https://steamcommunity.com/app/102820/discussions/0/648814845292513057/;

If you haven't bought the game yet though I would suggest just buying it off Origin.
